done, then so be it.

510
01:00:17,770 --> 01:00:22,870
That's my mother's Trident,
powerful but flawed like her.

511
01:00:22,910 --> 01:00:25,750
I wield my father's.

512
01:00:25,750 --> 01:00:28,720
And it has never known defeat!

513
01:01:16,760 --> 01:01:18,930
I promised Atlanna I'll protect him.

514
01:01:25,910 --> 01:01:30,710
This isn't a competition.
It's an execution.

515
01:03:25,890 --> 01:03:30,800
I am the one true king!

516
01:04:12,940 --> 01:04:16,000
You waiting for an invitation? Get in!

517
01:04:25,820 --> 01:04:28,790
Mera!

518
01:04:31,890 --> 01:04:35,850
So what's the plan?- The plan was to recover
Atlan's Trident. Then challenge Orm.

519
01:04:35,900 --> 01:04:38,800
Ok. So we do things not in order.
Shit happens.

520
01:04:43,870 --> 01:04:47,710
Heads up. We got a bogey on our six.-
What does that even mean?

521
01:04:47,740 --> 01:04:49,770
Bad guys behind us.- We just did that.

522
01:04:49,780 --> 01:04:50,940
Bad guys behind us.

523
01:05:58,810 --> 01:06:01,750
Woah, woah, wait. You said we
shouldn't go over these walls-I did.

524
01:06:01,750 --> 01:06:03,810
We shouldn't hide these things.-
I did! Now shut up!

525
01:06:37,720 --> 01:06:40,780
We are not dead yet!

526
01:06:41,820 --> 01:06:43,920
Jump!

527
