Here, hold this.

528
01:06:53,870 --> 01:06:56,740
What are you doing?-
We're gonna follow Pinnochio.

529
01:06:56,770 --> 01:06:58,970
Who?- Never mind, come here.
Get in. Come on.

530
01:07:01,010 --> 01:07:03,940
Great. So we are getting eaten.

531
01:07:25,800 --> 01:07:28,960
How'd you even doing this
anyway?- I don't know.

532
01:07:28,970 --> 01:07:34,840
I can hear them sometimes. They can hear me-
Right. We're both is some animal stomach.

533
01:07:34,840 --> 01:07:35,900
Hey, I just saved your life.

534
01:07:35,940 --> 01:07:37,710
I saved yours first.

535
01:07:41,880 --> 01:07:46,720
He said, coast is clear.
So, where to now?

536
01:07:47,720 --> 01:07:50,780
To the ocean of sand, your
people called the Sahara.

537
01:07:51,890 --> 01:07:53,720
Right.

538
01:08:20,820 --> 01:08:21,810
Thanks for the ride buddy.

539
01:08:25,860 --> 01:08:27,760
Are you ok?

540
01:08:27,900 --> 01:08:30,830
I've never been so high up.

541
01:08:31,770 --> 01:08:33,930
We're so far from home.

542
01:08:34,900 --> 01:08:36,960
At least you have a home.

543
01:08:36,970 --> 01:08:40,770
Not anymore. I can never go back.

544
01:08:40,780 --> 01:08:43,870
I betrayed everything when I
saved you at the Coliseum.

545
01:08:47,850 --> 01:08:50,940
Kalau begitu, I have to take you back.

546
01:08:50,990 --> 01:08:53,960
Atlantis is many wonderful things.

547
01:08:53,990 --> 01:08:56,960
But forgiving does not.-
But you're royalty.

548
01:08:56,990 --> 01:08:58,930
So is your mother.

549
01:08:59,730 --> 01:09:02,750
