for the Trench.

550
01:09:02,760 --> 01:09:05,730
Even my own father wouldn't take me back.

551
01:09:08,940 --> 01:09:13,930
Look on the bright side. You don't have
to marry someone you're obligated.

552
01:09:13,940 --> 01:09:16,780
Obligation isn't love.

553
01:09:16,810 --> 01:09:19,840
This is my family and my nation.

554
01:09:19,850 --> 01:09:21,940
And I've turned my back on both.

555
01:09:23,920 --> 01:09:26,950
Sometimes we have to do what's right,

556
01:09:26,950 --> 01:09:30,890
even if your heart aches against it.

557
01:09:45,710 --> 01:09:48,770
Your Highness.

558
01:09:49,740 --> 01:09:51,800
The tracking puts Princess Mera here.

559
01:09:51,910 --> 01:09:53,940
In the desert.

560
01:09:53,980 --> 01:09:58,720
You aid she was dead.- Apparently not.

561
01:09:59,850 --> 01:10:02,760
Does your brother still lives as well?-
Not for long.

562
01:10:02,760 --> 01:10:05,820
Captain Murk, assemble the
strike force immediately.- No!

563
01:10:05,830 --> 01:10:08,960
Mira is to be arrested
and she returned to me.

564
01:10:08,960 --> 01:10:10,730
